rojunction. The high mobility of the 2DEG is mainly due\nto the small electron effective mass in GAO/STO heterostructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 18:04:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Feb 2022 08:18:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-15"}
