aunch), e-ASTROGAM and AMEGO in the\nHE range. Still, possible ALP-induced effects on photon polarization could also\nbe detected by IXPE (already operative) and by the proposed eXTP, XL-Calibur,\nNGXP and XPP in the X-ray band.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 18:36:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 May 2023 17:12:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
