d\ncast $\\hat{\\vJ}$ as a \"spherical hybrid momentum\", a bit awkward for the\nconcept is novel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Feb 2022 03:15:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-28"}
