ion that all used mixed-integer\nprogramming and the Gurobi solver to schedule both the activities and the\nbattery use. The code and data used for the paper are publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Feb 2022 10:18:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 May 2022 08:42:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-27"}
